thread.title: Lunastal restaurant
thread.title_full: Retail Merchant Services reviewed by Lunastal restaurant

author: Lunastal restaurant
title: Lunastal restaurant
text:
Great saving by switching from WorldPay, excellent response from signing to receiving terminal. Ian Fyfe responded same day to visit and install terminal on a Friday night which was crucial for me as a restaurant as my old WorldPay one had broken down so that was a life saver!
Terminal all installed and ready for the weekends trading, Thank you Ian Fyfe and RMS
Highly recommended!
